cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL

The paper proposes a framework for optimizing deep neural networks using a combination of stochastic gradient descent and evolutionary algorithms. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and optimization (cs.NE). The use of evolutionary algorithms also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The applications mentioned in the paper, such as speech recognition and image recognition, suggest a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
